{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CSS 選擇器","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/CSS_Selector","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>CSS 選擇器</strong>是 CSS 規則的一部分。它能讓你選定要調整哪個（或哪些）元素的樣式。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"範例","title":"範例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> I am inside of a div element. <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> I am inside of a paragraph element. <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> green<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>在第一個 CSS 規則，我選取了 <code>&lt;div&gt;</code> 元素、並將該元素的文字變成了綠色。在第二個 CSS 規則，我選取了 <code>&lt;p&gt;</code> 元素、並將該元素的文字變成了紅色。結果應該長成這個樣子：</p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"範例 sample\" id=\"frame_範例\" width=\"640\" height=\"80\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/CSS_Selector/_sample_.%E7%AF%84%E4%BE%8B.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"深入理解","title":"深入理解","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本知識","title":"基本知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>基本選擇器\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/Type_selectors\">類型選擇器</a> <code>elementname</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Class_selectors\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Class 選擇器 (en-US)</a> <code>.classname</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/ID_selectors\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">ID 選擇器 (en-US)</a> <code>#idname</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Universal_selectors\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">通用選擇器 (en-US)</a> <code>* ns|* *|*</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Attribute_selectors\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">屬性選擇器 (en-US)</a> <code>[attr=value]</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/Pseudo-classes\">狀態選擇器</a> <code>a:active, a:visited</code></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n  <li>複合選擇器\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Adjacent_sibling_combinator\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">鄰接同層選擇器 (en-US)</a> <code>A + B</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/General_sibling_combinator\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">通用同層選擇器 (en-US)</a> <code>A ~ B</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Child_combinator\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">直屬選擇器 (en-US)</a> <code>A &gt; B</code></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/Descendant_combinator\">後代選擇器</a> <code>A B</code></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Pseudo-elements\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">虛擬元素 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/CSS/Pseudo-classes\">虛擬類別</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"範例","id":"範例"},{"text":"深入理解","id":"深入理解"}],"summary":"CSS 選擇器是 CSS 規則的一部分。它能讓你選定要調整哪個（或哪些）元素的樣式。","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Selector (CSS)","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Sélecteur CSS","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Selector (セレクター (CSS) )","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Selector (CSS)","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"CSS-селектор","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"CSS 选择器","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/glossary/css_selector","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/glossary/css_selector/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary","title":"術語表"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/CSS_Selector","title":"CSS 選擇器"}],"pageTitle":"CSS 選擇器 - 術語表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}